<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="nl">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Avondmaal Cheatsheet — 1600 kcal</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@700;900&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --cream: #faf6ef;
    --warm: #f0e8d8;
    --accent: #c8531a;
    --accent2: #4a7c59;
    --accent3: #2d5fa6;
    --dark: #1e1812;
    --mid: #6b5744;
    --rule: #d9cabb;
    --tag-bg: #eee4d4;
  }

  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

  body {
    background: var(--cream);
    color: var(--dark);
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 300;
    min-height: 100vh;
  }

  .page {
    max-width: 860px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 48px 32px 80px;
  }

  /* ── HEADER ── */
  header {
    border-top: 3px solid var(--dark);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
    padding: 28px 0 22px;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-end;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 20px;
  }

  .header-left h1 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 2.8rem;
    line-height: 1;
    color: var(--dark);
    letter-spacing: -0.5px;
  }

  .header-left .sub {
    margin-top: 6px;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--mid);
  }

  .kcal-badge {
    background: var(--accent);
    color: white;
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 1.6rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    padding: 12px 22px;
    line-height: 1;
    text-align: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .kcal-badge small {
    display: block;
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-top: 4px;
    opacity: 0.85;
  }

  /* ── GRID LAYOUT ── */
  .grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 24px;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
  }

  .grid-3 {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 18px;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
  }

  /* ── CARDS ── */
  .card {
    background: var(--warm);
    border: 1px solid var(--rule);
    padding: 22px 22px 20px;
  }

  .card-full {
    background: var(--warm);
    border: 1px solid var(--rule);
    padding: 22px 26px 20px;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
  }

  .card h2, .card-full h2 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: var(--dark);
    margin-bottom: 14px;
    padding-bottom: 8px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
  }

  .card h2 span, .card-full h2 span {
    display: inline-block;
    width: 10px;
    height: 10px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    margin-right: 8px;
    vertical-align: middle;
    position: relative;
    top: -1px;
  }

  .dot-red { background: var(--accent); }
  .dot-green { background: var(--accent2); }
  .dot-blue { background: var(--accent3); }

  /* ── VERDELING AVONDMAAL ── */
  .portion-row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    padding: 7px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px dashed var(--rule);
    font-size: 0.88rem;
  }

  .portion-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }

  .portion-icon {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    width: 28px;
    text-align: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .portion-label { flex: 1; color: var(--dark); }

  .portion-kcal {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--accent);
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  /* ── KOOLHYDRATEN TABEL ── */
  .kh-table {
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: collapse;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
  }

  .kh-table th {
    text-align: left;
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--mid);
    padding: 0 0 8px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
  }

  .kh-table td {
    padding: 9px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px dashed var(--rule);
    vertical-align: middle;
  }

  .kh-table tr:last-child td { border-bottom: none; }

  .kh-name {
    font-weight: 500;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  .kh-icon { font-size: 1.1rem; }

  .kh-amount { color: var(--mid); font-size: 0.82rem; }

  .kh-kcal {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    color: var(--accent);
    text-align: right;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  /* ── VUISTREGEL ── */
  .rule-row {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0;
    background: var(--dark);
    color: white;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
  }

  .rule-label {
    background: var(--accent);
    padding: 16px 20px;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    writing-mode: vertical-rl;
    text-orientation: mixed;
    transform: rotate(180deg);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .rule-items {
    display: flex;
    flex: 1;
    gap: 0;
  }

  .rule-item {
    flex: 1;
    padding: 18px 20px;
    border-left: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
  }

  .rule-item:first-child { border-left: none; }

  .rule-item .ri-name {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }

  .rule-item .ri-amount {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    color: white;
  }

  .rule-item .ri-note {
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
    margin-top: 3px;
  }

  /* ── VOORBEELDEN ── */
  .examples-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
  }

  .example-card {
    border: 1px solid var(--rule);
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .example-header {
    padding: 10px 14px 9px;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 2.5px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: white;
  }

  .ex-vis { background: var(--accent3); }
  .ex-kip { background: var(--accent2); }
  .ex-vlees { background: var(--accent); }

  .example-body {
    background: var(--warm);
    padding: 14px;
  }

  .ex-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 7px;
    font-size: 0.84rem;
    color: var(--dark);
    line-height: 1.35;
  }

  .ex-item:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }

  .ex-dot {
    width: 5px;
    height: 5px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    margin-top: 6px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .ex-item .ex-kcal {
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    color: var(--mid);
    display: block;
    margin-top: 1px;
  }

  .ex-total {
    margin-top: 10px;
    padding-top: 8px;
    border-top: 1px dashed var(--rule);
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--accent);
    text-align: right;
  }

  /* ── TIPS ── */
  .tips-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 18px;
  }

  .tip-card {
    background: var(--warm);
    border: 1px solid var(--rule);
    padding: 18px 20px;
  }

  .tip-card h3 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    padding-bottom: 7px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
    color: var(--dark);
  }

  .tip-item {
    display: flex;
    gap: 9px;
    align-items: flex-start;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
    font-size: 0.84rem;
    line-height: 1.4;
    color: var(--dark);
  }

  .tip-item:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }

  .tip-arrow {
    color: var(--accent2);
    font-weight: 700;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 1px;
  }

  /* ── FOOTER ── */
  footer {
    margin-top: 48px;
    padding-top: 16px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--rule);
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    color: var(--mid);
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .grid, .grid-3, .examples-grid, .tips-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .rule-items { flex-direction: column; }
    .rule-item { border-left: none; border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); }
    header { flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; }
    .header-left h1 { font-size: 2rem; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="page">

  <!-- HEADER -->
  <header>
    <div class="header-left">
      <h1>Avondmaal<br>Cheatsheet</h1>
      <div class="sub">Dagdieet — gebalanceerde richtlijnen</div>
    </div>
    <div class="kcal-badge">
      1600
      <small>kcal / dag</small>
    </div>
  </header>

  <!-- ROW 1: Verdeling + Koolhydraten -->
  <div class="grid">

    <div class="card">
      <h2><span class="dot-red"></span>Avondmaal: 400–600 kcal</h2>
      <div class="portion-row">
        <div class="portion-icon">🥩</div>
        <div class="portion-label">Vlees (mager)</div>
        <div class="portion-kcal">100 g · 120–180 kcal</div>
      </div>
      <div class="portion-row">
        <div class="portion-icon">🐟</div>
        <div class="portion-label">Vis (mager)</div>
        <div class="portion-kcal">150 g · 120–220 kcal</div>
      </div>
      <div class="portion-row">
        <div class="portion-icon">🥦</div>
        <div class="portion-label">Groenten</div>
        <div class="portion-kcal">250–400 g · 50–120 kcal</div>
      </div>
      <div class="portion-row">
        <div class="portion-icon">🍚</div>
        <div class="portion-label">Koolhydraten</div>
        <div class="portion-kcal">zie tabel →</div>
      </div>
      <div class="portion-row">
        <div class="portion-icon">🫒</div>
        <div class="portion-label">Olie (optioneel)</div>
        <div class="portion-kcal">1 tl · ~40 kcal</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h2><span class="dot-blue"></span>Koolhydraten richtlijn</h2>
      <table class="kh-table">
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th>Product</th>
            <th>Hoeveelheid</th>
            <th style="text-align:right">kcal</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr>
            <td>
              <div class="kh-name">
                <span class="kh-icon">🍚</span> Rijst
              </div>
            </td>
            <td><span class="kh-amount">50–70 g ongekookt</span></td>
            <td class="kh-kcal">180–250</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>
              <div class="kh-name">
                <span class="kh-icon">🍝</span> Pasta
              </div>
            </td>
            <td><span class="kh-amount">60–80 g ongekookt</span></td>
            <td class="kh-kcal">210–290</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>
              <div class="kh-name">
                <span class="kh-icon">🥔</span> Aardappel
              </div>
            </td>
            <td><span class="kh-amount">200–300 g gekookt</span></td>
            <td class="kh-kcal">150–240</td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- VUISTREGEL BALK -->
  <div class="rule-row">
    <div class="rule-label">Veilige vuistregel</div>
    <div class="rule-items">
      <div class="rule-item">
        <div class="ri-name">🍚 Rijst</div>
        <div class="ri-amount">60 g</div>
        <div class="ri-note">droog / ongekookt</div>
      </div>
      <div class="rule-item">
        <div class="ri-name">🍝 Pasta</div>
        <div class="ri-amount">70 g</div>
        <div class="ri-note">droog / ongekookt</div>
      </div>
      <div class="rule-item">
        <div class="ri-name">🥔 Aardappelen</div>
        <div class="ri-amount">250 g</div>
        <div class="ri-note">gekookt gewicht</div>
      </div>
      <div class="rule-item">
        <div class="ri-name">🎯 Totaal avond</div>
        <div class="ri-amount">450–600</div>
        <div class="ri-note">kcal doelzone</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- VOORBEELDEN -->
  <div class="card-full">
    <h2><span class="dot-green"></span>Praktische maaltijdvoorbeelden</h2>
    <div class="examples-grid">

      <!-- Vis -->
      <div class="example-card">
        <div class="example-header ex-vis">🐟 Vis — Kabeljauw</div>
        <div class="example-body">
          <div class="ex-item">
            <div class="ex-dot" style="background:var(--accent3)"></div>
            <div>150 g kabeljauw<span class="ex-kcal">~120 kcal</span></div>
          </div>
          <div class="ex-item">
            <div class="ex-dot" style="background:var(--accent3)"></div>
            <div>250 g aardappelen (gek.)<span class="ex-kcal">~190 kcal</span></div>
          </div>
          <div class="ex-item">
            <div class="ex-dot" style="background:var(--accent3)"></div>
            <div>300 g broccoli + citroen<span class="ex-kcal">~75 kcal</span></div>
          </div>
          <div class="ex-item">
            <div class="ex-dot" style="background:var(--accent3)"></div>
            <div>1 tl olijfolie<span class="ex-kcal">~40 kcal</span></div>
          </div>
          <div class="ex-total">≈ 425 kcal</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Kip -->
      <div class="example-card">
        <div class="example-header ex-kip">🍗 Gevogelte — Kipfilet</div>
        <div class="example-body">
          <div class="ex-item">
            <div class="ex-dot" style="background:var(--accent2)"></div>
            <div>100 g kipfilet<span class="ex-kcal">~110 kcal</span></div>
          </div>
          <div class="ex-item">
            <div class="ex-dot" style="background:var(--accent2)"></div>
            <div>60 g rijst ongekookt<span class="ex-kcal">~215 kcal</span></div>
          </div>
          <div class="ex-item">
            <div class="ex-dot" style="background:var(--accent2)"></div>
            <div>300 g wokgroenten<span class="ex-kcal">~80 kcal</span></div>
          </div>
          <div class="ex-item">
            <div class="ex-dot" style="background:var(--accent2)"></div>
            <div>sojasaus + knoflook<span class="ex-kcal">~15 kcal</span></div>
          </div>
          <div class="ex-total">≈ 420 kcal</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Vlees -->
      <div class="example-card">
        <div class="example-header ex-vlees">🥩 Vlees — Mager gehakt</div>
        <div class="example-body">
          <div class="ex-item">
            <div class="ex-dot" style="background:var(--accent)"></div>
            <div>100 g mager gehakt<span class="ex-kcal">~160 kcal</span></div>
          </div>
          <div class="ex-item">
            <div class="ex-dot" style="background:var(--accent)"></div>
            <div>70 g pasta ongekookt<span class="ex-kcal">~250 kcal</span></div>
          </div>
          <div class="ex-item">
            <div class="ex-dot" style="background:var(--accent)"></div>
            <div>tomatensaus + courgette<span class="ex-kcal">~60 kcal</span></div>
          </div>
          <div class="ex-item">
            <div class="ex-dot" style="background:var(--accent)"></div>
            <div>kruiden, geen extra vet<span class="ex-kcal">0 kcal</span></div>
          </div>
          <div class="ex-total">≈ 470 kcal</div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- TIPS -->
  <div class="tips-grid">
    <div class="tip-card">
      <h3>🥦 Extra verzadiging, minder calorieën</h3>
      <div class="tip-item">
        <span class="tip-arrow">→</span>
        Kies aardappelen boven pasta voor meer vulling
      </div>
      <div class="tip-item">
        <span class="tip-arrow">→</span>
        Voeg altijd veel groenten toe als volumevuller
      </div>
      <div class="tip-item">
        <span class="tip-arrow">→</span>
        Gebruik magere sauzen: tomaat, yoghurt, bouillon
      </div>
      <div class="tip-item">
        <span class="tip-arrow">→</span>
        Werk met kruiden en specerijen i.p.v. vet
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="tip-card">
      <h3>🐟 Beste keuzes vlees & vis</h3>
      <div class="tip-item">
        <span class="tip-arrow">→</span>
        <strong>Vis:</strong> kabeljauw, heek, tilapia, forel (~70–100 kcal/100g)
      </div>
      <div class="tip-item">
        <span class="tip-arrow">→</span>
        <strong>Gevogelte:</strong> kipfilet, kalkoen (~100–130 kcal/100g)
      </div>
      <div class="tip-item">
        <span class="tip-arrow">→</span>
        <strong>Rood vlees:</strong> mager rundergehakt, biefstuk (~130–180 kcal/100g)
      </div>
      <div class="tip-item">
        <span class="tip-arrow">→</span>
        Vermijd gepaneerd, gebakken of vette bereidingen
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <footer>
    <span>AVONDMAAL CHEATSHEET · 1600 KCAL DAGDIEET</span>
    <span>Indicatieve waarden · consult een diëtist voor persoonlijk advies</span>
  </footer>

</div>
</body>
</html>
